data.name: chckSpam.ToolTip
data.value:
When you use a fast sender it will send the messages very quickly. This works fine in chats like Skype, and webbrowsers. When you're chatting in Shockwave or Adobe air programs, such as Hipchat, disable this to make it work better.
This option sends multiple breaks, so don't disable this if you can send empty messages.
